be key-coded and encrypted.


500
00:19:18.124 --> 00:19:19.658 line:-1 position:50%
Next, you should be transparent


501
00:19:19.658 --> 00:19:22.561 line:-1 position:50%
about the information
you are collecting and why.


502
00:19:22.561 --> 00:19:25.164 line:-1 position:50%
Anytime you request to read
a certain HealthKit type,


503
00:19:25.164 --> 00:19:27.533 line:-1 position:50%
we'll prompt the user
to approve its use.


504
00:19:27,533 --> 00:19:30,636 line:-1
But beyond this basic measure,
it's our joint responsibility


505
00:19:30,636 --> 00:19:32,772 line:-1
to collect only
the most meaningful data


506
00:19:32.772 --> 00:19:36.075 line:-1 position:50%
and to be transparent
on how that data will be used.


507
00:19:36,075 --> 00:19:38,811 line:-1
For example,
