collected from them.


520
00:20:06,639 --> 00:20:08,741 line:-1
If you take data
outside of HealthKit,


521
00:20:08.741 --> 00:20:11.744 line:-1 position:50%
your customer should have
an easy way to view and delete,


522
00:20:11,744 --> 00:20:13,379 line:-1
turn off data collection,


523
00:20:13,379 --> 00:20:15,414 line:-1
or have other means
to exercise control


524
00:20:15.414 --> 00:20:17.616 line:-1 position:50%
over what is collected
from them.


525
00:20:17,616 --> 00:20:19,552 line:-1
Whether you are using
Walking Steadiness


